<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>&quot;The Bowe Decommission, Part Three&quot;</strong><br />
And your toys are my toys and my toys are your toys&#8230;</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/this-page-intentionally-left-blank">More by this author!</a></strong></p>
</div>
